race.comment: REVVED UP (1) boasts a strong record this journey with 11 wins and three minors from 23 tries. Missed the frame latest (20.22) when seventh over 350m at this track in a NG. Rates on top and should go close. PURE BLUE (7) placed last time (25.24) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 3.5 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. AUSSIE BLEND (3) finished well back at this track last time when a 10 length fifth (20.25) but scored four back at this track (19.83). Returns to favourable track. Has ability and can measure up. POCKET RAIDER (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.
